<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Processing Complete - Cancer Data Platform</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4a6fdc;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4a6fdc;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .file-info {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>File Processing Complete</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello,</p>
    
    <p>We're pleased to inform you that your file processing task has been completed successfully.</p>
    
    {{#if fileInfo}}
    <div class="file-info">
      <h3>Processed File Details:</h3>
      <p><strong>Processed Files:</strong> {{fileInfo.fileCount}}</p>
      {{#if fileInfo.fileName}}
      <p><strong>File Name:</strong> {{fileInfo.fileName}}</p>
      {{/if}}
      {{#if fileInfo.processedAt}}
      <p><strong>Processed At:</strong> {{formatDate fileInfo.processedAt}}</p>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    {{/if}}
    
    <p>You can now download the processed file by clicking the button below:</p>
    
    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{downloadLink}}" class="button">Download Your File</a>
    </p>
    
    {{#if additionalInfo}}
    <p>Additional Information: {{additionalInfo}}</p>
    {{/if}}
    
    <p>Thank you for using our platform.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    Cancer Data Platform Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
    <p>&copy; {{formatDate now 'YYYY'}} Cancer Data Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>